Title: GroupDocs.Assembly Visual Studio Plugin
Description: This plugin will download all the GroupDocs.Assembly examples from the source control for you.
HomeWiki:
Project Description
This plugin will download all the GroupDocs.Assembly examples from the source control for you.
This plugin is providing an ease to compile GroupDocs.Assembly for .NET 3.0.0 examples. It has reduced the efforts to download examples and DLL file from different resources.

Features

Plugin accommodates the user with following features/steps

- Automatically download GroupDocs.Assembly DLL file
- Add GroupDocs.Assembly reference automatically
- Clone/download example from GitHub for you
- Gives you option to open a project (CSharp or Visual Basic)
- Supports Visual Studio 2010, 2012 and 2013
You may need to add Newtonsoft.Json.DLL as reference in order to build any of the project (C# or VB).

See how to install the plugin via video demonstration.
